thread.title: Engines found at site of Russian plane crash

title: Engines found at site of Russian plane crash
text:
Engines found at site of Russian plane crash 5:09pm GMT - 00:52 
The engines of the plane that crashed near Moscow have been recovered, as investigators make progress on what caused the plane to go down killing all 71 people on board. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
